Version 2.4 - 2025-05-12
  * Added 36 new coins. Current total: 119 coins.
  * Added a timeout to declarer lost connection, displaying ERR for this event.
  * Allowing up to 8 decimal places instead of 4.
  * Updated README.md.

Version 2.3 - 2025-05-03
  * Added 8 new coins.
  * Added Price Multiplier option.
  * Added optional thousands separator.
  * Added optional swap commas-dots.
  * Added vertical scroll bar for configuration screen to be displayed when needed.
  * Added script check-top-100.sh to improve the searching for new coins.
  * Updated README.md.

Version 2.2 - 2025-04-30
  * Added a refresh time option. The value is between 1 and 60 minutes.
  * Added a blinking on price refresh option.
  * Updated README.md.

Version 2.1 - 2025-04-21
  * Increased delay of the click price update.
  * Implemented colors. Now, users can apply colors to prices.
  * Updated README.md.

Version 2.0 - 2025-04-19
  * Migrated from CoinGecko API to Binance API.
      -  Binance API is faster than CoinGecko API.
      -  Binance API has less limitations. It is possible to access several pairs of coins at the same time.
      -  In April 18, 2025, CoinGecko API was providing 100 coins under USD, while Binance had 573 under USDT.
  * Added 36 new coins and 10 new currencies.
  * Returning 'Err' on errors, in the price area.
  * Updating the price when clicking over it.

Version 1.2.1 - 2025-04-16
  * UNRELEASED.
  * Improved documentation.
  * The last version under CoinGecko. Migrating to Binance...

Version 1.2 - 2025-04-16
  * Added 24 new coins.
  * Improved README.md.
  * Simplified infos on Configuration window.

Version 1.1 - 2025-04-15
  * Changed the main icon.
  * Added instructions how to install importing a tarball
    (present in the source code only, README.md).

Version 1.0 - 2025-04-15
  * Initial version.
